  CIA triad:
Confidentiality: Only the people who supposed to see it, should see it.
Integrity: no change, if there is change it must be authorized.
Availability: Available to those who should be available it to. 
  Expansion:
Authenticity: Authentic, legit.
Non-repudiation: can't deny who did it.


Red team: Attacker, pentester, vulnerability assessor, Ethical Hacker
Blue team: Defenders
